✍️ Typography
Token	Font	Usage
--font-family-base	'Inter', sans-serif	Base font
--font-size-xs	12px	Captions, labels
--font-size-sm	14px	Inputs, secondary text
--font-size-md	16px	Default body text
--font-size-lg	20px	Subheadings
--font-size-xl	24px	Titles
--font-size-xxl	32px	Main headers

Font weights:

Regular (400) → body text

Medium (500) → labels

Bold (700) → headings
